These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, water
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, camping, gardening, skydiving, filmmaking, writing, photography
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, sports, western, crime, adventure, satire, romance
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
15. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
16. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
17. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
19. the person watching western movies is in the middle##1
20. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Beverage      | fanta    | 7up     | water  | lemonade   | iced-tea | juice      | cola          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| Hobby         | reading | camping | filmmaking | writing | gardening   | skydiving     | photography |
| Movie-Genre     | romance      | satire   | spy   | western  | crime  | adventure | sports       |

