 3. the person watching romance movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
 5. the analyst is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the freelancer##1
 9. the person who likes red is the coach##1
10. the fan of techno is in the middle##1
11. the coach is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the fan of blues is the person who likes emerald##1
13. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
14. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
15. the engineer is on the right of the social-worker##1
16. the fan of blues is the person who likes emerald##1
17. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the dancer##1
18. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of soul##1
19. the person who likes chestnut is the person watching comedy movies##1
20. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
